  m_text: "Curses: Curses are obtained from crystalized monkey paws..  If the eyeball
    hits one the player is then cursed, bringing a positive and negative effect.
    \n\nIncludes: Growing giant but having gravity, two balls but one looks identical
    after a bit, and a punch move that makes the ball move straight and faster!"
